# Social Media Campaign Performance Tracker

## Project Overview

This project analyzes the performance of various marketing channels and advertising campaigns using Power BI. The objective is to evaluate marketing effectiveness, compare channel performance, calculate ROI, and generate business insights to optimize advertising investments.

This project was completed as part of the Future Interns Data Science & Analytics Internship.

---

## Objectives

- Analyze marketing campaign performance.
- Compare advertising channels.
- Track sales and advertising spend.
- Measure Return on Investment (ROI).
- Identify top-performing marketing channels.
- Generate actionable business recommendations.

---

## Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Power BI
- Microsoft Excel

---

## Dataset

Dataset: Advertising Data

The dataset contains marketing spend across different advertising channels and corresponding sales performance.

### Features

- TV Advertising Spend
- Billboards Spend
- Google Ads Spend
- Social Media Spend
- Influencer Marketing Spend
- Affiliate Marketing Spend
- Product Sales

---

## Analysis Performed

### Data Cleaning
- Imported and validated dataset.
- Checked data quality and consistency.
- Prepared data for visualization.

### Marketing Performance Analysis
- Total Sales Analysis
- Total Marketing Spend Analysis
- ROI Analysis
- Channel-wise Performance Analysis
- Marketing Spend Distribution
- Campaign Effectiveness Evaluation

### Dashboard Development

Created an interactive Power BI dashboard including:

- KPI Cards
- Total Sales
- Total Spend
- Profit Analysis
- ROI Tracking
- Channel Performance Charts
- Marketing Spend Distribution
- Interactive Filters

---

## Key Insights

- Marketing performance varies significantly across channels.
- Certain channels generate higher returns with lower investment.
- ROI analysis helps identify the most efficient advertising platforms.
- Advertising spend distribution highlights budget allocation patterns.
- Data-driven marketing decisions can improve campaign effectiveness.

---

## Business Recommendations

- Increase investment in high-performing channels.
- Optimize budget allocation based on ROI.
- Monitor underperforming campaigns regularly.
- Focus on channels with strong conversion performance.
- Use performance analytics to improve future campaign planning.

